<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 14:02:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加密货币监管推动打破了长期的政治联盟</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-12/crypto-regulatory-push-shatters-long-standing-political-alliances</link><description>稳定币之争导致了奇怪的同床异梦。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieWvLUhe0wsQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-12/crypto-regulatory-push-shatters-long-standing-political-alliances</guid></item><item><title>德意志银行、纳斯达克以 1.2 亿美元投资加密货币公司 Elliptic</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-12/deutsche-bank-nasdaq-back-crypto-firm-elliptic-in-120-million-round</link><description>随着大型金融机构扩大其数字资产产品，区块链分析公司 Elliptic Enterprises Ltd. 在德意志银行和纳斯达克风险投资部门支持的新一轮融资中筹集了 1.2 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCqW.PPVqQts/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-12/deutsche-bank-nasdaq-back-crypto-firm-elliptic-in-120-million-round</guid></item><item><title>华尔街将区块链应用于 13 万亿美元的回购市场</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-05-12/jpmorgan-wall-street-use-blockchain-in-13-trillion-repo-market</link><description>摩根大通公司在十多年来花费了数亿美元开发使用区块链的系统，这种新技术本应从根本上颠覆金融市场，但尚未成为游戏规则的改变者。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.D_zKuGccy4/v1/1200x-1.gif" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 11:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-05-12/jpmorgan-wall-street-use-blockchain-in-13-trillion-repo-market</guid></item><item><title>安静的代币销售使特朗普的加密货币财富增加了 6.6 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-12/quiet-token-sales-boosted-trump-crypto-wealth-by-660-million</link><description>根据彭博亿万富翁指数，特朗普家族成员通过销售 World Liberty Financial Inc. 代币赚取了约 15.5 亿美元，在考虑到之前未披露的交易后，他们的总财富增加了约 6.6 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPBYHgXplowc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 10:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-12/quiet-token-sales-boosted-trump-crypto-wealth-by-660-million</guid></item><item><title>法国 NBA 球星支持的加密货币公司停止购买比特币的计划</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-12/crypto-firm-backed-by-french-nba-star-halts-plan-to-buy-bitcoin</link><description>比特币协会是一家由法国 NBA 球星 Tony Parker 和企业家 Éric Larchevêque 支持的初创公司，在宣布该战略几个月后，该公司放弃了建立加密货币金库的计划。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV5g_Gt6k1EE/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 05:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-12/crypto-firm-backed-by-french-nba-star-halts-plan-to-buy-bitcoin</guid></item><item><title>由于对自己的区块链和立法的乐观情绪，Circle 激增</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-11/circle-s-first-quarter-revenue-increases-20-net-income-drops</link><description>由于人们对稳定币发行人 ARC 区块链项目的前景持乐观态度，并且美国立法者开始考虑一项具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，Circle Internet Group Inc. 的股价上涨了 14%。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iHMGucUQHtCk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 10:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-11/circle-s-first-quarter-revenue-increases-20-net-income-drops</guid></item><item><title>参议员关注具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，银行和加密货币支持者发生争执</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/banks-and-crypto-backers-tussle-as-senators-eye-stablecoin-bill</link><description>随着参议院一个重要小组开始考虑一项具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，银行集团正在最后一刻对稳定币收益率进行妥协。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWhBANxj4P6o/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 23:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/banks-and-crypto-backers-tussle-as-senators-eye-stablecoin-bill</guid></item></channel></rss>